                            <comment id="431719" author="flei" created="Wed, 16 Oct 2024 23:45:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Due to the special configuration of parallel-scale-nfs test suite, lustre fs is mounted at MDS, then exported as nfs share to all clients. In this case, the MDS is still at old version 2.15.5, so this test case fails. Skip this test case if MDS is at old version to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="431310" author="flei" created="Mon, 14 Oct 2024 08:01:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is so similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18030&quot; title=&quot;ll_set_acl eats permissions if they could be expressed with mode bits&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18030&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18030&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; but &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18030&quot; title=&quot;ll_set_acl eats permissions if they could be expressed with mode bits&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18030&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18030&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is a client only bug and has been fixed in master.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
